<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lys ạ̹lạ qṭrẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lys ạ̹lạ qṭrẗ mn ḥbk qṭrẗ.
 ltṣbḥ fy qlby ạlṣgẖyr mḥyṭ ḥb kbyr.
 fy gẖmrẗ kl ạlnfws.tlqy̱ ạrtwạʾ whnạʾ
 ʿwḍ kl ạlẓmạ̉ ʿwḍ kl sẖqạʾ
 lys ạ̹lạ wmḍẗ mn nạrk rby wmḍẗ
 ltṣbḥ fy qlby ạlʿqym ạ̉twn nạr ʿẓym.
 fy gẖmrh kl ạlnfws.tlqy̱ ạldfʾ wạlʿzạʾ
 ʿwḍ ạlbrd wạlʿnạʾ..qṭrẗ mn ḥbk
 lys ạ̹lạ brʿmạaⁿ mn ḥlqk brʿmạ.
 lyṣbḥ qlby ạlʿlyl bstạn ḥb ʿlyl</lyrics>
<hymn_number>10489</hymn_number>
</song>